dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:10,000 scale maps of Chiba (Japan), titled 'Ichimanbun no ichi chikeizu Shimoshizu oyobi Narashinohara kinbō -- 一万分一地形圖下志津及習志野原近傍/Ichimanbun no ichi chikeizu Shimoshizu oyobi Narashinohara kinbō.’ To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Stanford University Libraries, Stanford Geospatial Center
